{"tid":2290490,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"李家超：若港人對港區國安法抱質疑或做錯決定","createTime":"2020-11-18T04:57:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-18T06:48:49.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"a3ac4a6b8841e005f92aed981fbb4a1cfc47afac","tid":2290490,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T04:57:23.000Z","msg":"保安局局長李家超指，其他國家針對本港訂立《港區國安法》所採取的不合理措施，都是基於政治理由，認為在過渡期間有不穩定因素可以理解，又指如果現時港人對港區國安法抱有質疑，可能會作出很錯的決定。<br />\n<br />\n當局指，去年有約3.3萬人領取俗稱「良民證」的無犯罪紀錄証明書，比前年多1萬人，但未有披露今年的數字。 <br />\n<br />\n李家超在立法會回應議員質詢時指，至今並無雙邊經貿協議因為港區國安法的實施而被撤銷，亦無文化交流計劃因而暫停。<br />\n<br />\n他指，正常商業機構都會檢視香港是否仍然值得投資和發展，本港仍有低稅率、政府高效率等優勢，又以澳門為例，指2009年澳門訂立國安法後GDP大增。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2366792\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2366792&d=KoeRi8LHiva86SpHjnbz1TizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=297df95b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2366792</a>"},{"pid":"47516f70aaa6c008223e683a7639ff12973a1eb0","tid":2290490,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T04:59:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1560612-20201118.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1560612-20201118.htm&d=KoeRi8LHiva86SpHjnbz1TizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=672eeba3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1560612-20201118.htm&h=a690354a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1560612-20201118.htm</a>"},{"pid":"0af4cf587d06bbc5c5836985209a236dc3509ea5","tid":2290490,"uid":50386,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T04:59:38.000Z","msg":"澳門國安法立咗十幾年一次都冇用到<br />\n香港就個個星期都話呢個違反國安法嗰個違反國安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bb126ad1947fd882f6f2d2bbe71470a4566adbe","